Access Logging Made Easy With Envoy and Fluent Bit

Envoy
- mesh, deploys as side-car proxy
- decouples install and upgrade
- enables consistent config regardless of platform
AWS app mesh uses envoy proxy
- common need: manage inter-service traffic
- generate uniform logs, metrics and traces
- minimise impact on application code
- shift traffic between deployments
- decouple service teams
- application level networking
- works across compute services (ecs, fargate, eks, ec2, kubernetes on ec2)

Service team A -> Service team B

Fluent bit
- multi-platform log processor and forwarder
- lightweight and written in C